      <h2>KIC Events Diversity & Inclusion Policy</h2>
      <p>We are committed to fostering an inclusive, safe, and welcoming space for all individuals—regardless of kink, gender identity, sexual orientation, or relationship structure.</p>

      <h3>Respect & Inclusivity</h3>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>All-Gender & Pansexual-Friendly Space:</strong> Respect everyone’s self-identification and pronouns. Ask if you're unsure.</li>
        <li><strong>Your Kink May Not Be My Kink, and That’s OK:</strong> If something isn’t for you, quietly walk away. Do not criticize others’ scenes.</li>
        <li><strong>Open-Minded Exploration:</strong> Come with curiosity and respect for diverse experiences.</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>KIC Events Discrimination & Harassment Policy</h2>
      <p>We are committed to a safe, respectful, and inclusive environment. Discrimination, harassment, or inappropriate behavior is not tolerated.</p>

      <h3>Zero Tolerance for Discrimination & Harassment</h3>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>No Discrimination:</strong> Based on identity, orientation, structure, race, disability, religion, etc.</li>
        <li><strong>No Harassment:</strong> Unwanted advances, comments, intimidation, or boundary violations are forbidden. Consent is mandatory.</li>
        <li><strong>Respect Boundaries:</strong> Get explicit consent before engaging with anyone physically or verbally about play.</li>
      </ul>

      <h3>Reporting & Enforcement</h3>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Report:</strong> Speak to a MOD, staff, or email <a href="mailto:admin@kicevents.com">admin@kicevents.com</a>.</li>
        <li><strong>Violations:</strong> May result in warnings, ejection, or bans based on severity.</li>
        <li><strong>No Retaliation:</strong> Retaliation against reporters may result in a permanent ban.</li>
      </ul>

      <h3>Creating a Positive Space</h3>
      <p>KIC is a judgment-free environment grounded in consent and respect. Speak with staff if you experience or witness violations.</p>
      <p>By attending, you agree to help create a safer, more empowering community for everyone. Thank you for being part of KIC Events.</p>
